Captioned by
Media Access Group at WGBH

20:58.358 --> 21:00.293
I have to eat
this onion?

21:00.327 --> 21:02.261
-Honey, trust me.
-(sighs)

21:02.295 --> 21:06.132
Your mom knows.
It's time for you
to learn these secrets.

21:11.103 --> 21:13.906
-How does this help?
-It doesn't. Ha!

